{"id": "1510948004821995540", "channel_id": "1350058928020656178", "type": 19, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "None stands by your side is the traditionally grammartically correct choice, as \"None\" is derived from \"no one.\" \nBut treating it as a plural is indeed more common in everyday modern English: \"None stand by your side.\"\nWe decided to go with the traditional option for a more archaic, solemn vibe; we can adjust it so it fits most people's preference.<:agree:1400771815076528258>", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T10:07:56.406000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-01T10:10:03.507000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["205457916537470977"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💖", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1509152586920362005", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1350058928020656178", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【English Translation】Opinions Collection", "forum_channel_id": "1350027302205001779"}
